						<summary>

						<p>Records a similar gift of jewels as recorded in No. 8 above by Teṉ[ṉavaṉ] Brahmaśrīrājaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Nārāyaṇa ••• ••• raiyaṉ of Puḷḷamaṅgalam.</p>						

						<p>The record is dated in the reign of Parāntaka I. The regnal year may be any year between fortyone to forty-eight, the latest known regnal year for this king.</p>						

						</summary>
